description: Lanterns swing from lamppost situated at the corner of the var, their glaesine-paned windows glimmering in the sunlight.  Townsfolk hurry along the var, intent upon their business of the hour.

Lanterns swing from a tall lamppost situated at the corner of the var, their glaesine-paned windows glimmering with a deep golden hue.  A few passersby hurry along the var, intent upon their business of the hour.

Lanterns swing from lamppost situated at the corner of the var, their glaesine-paned windows glimmering with a deep golden hue.  A few passersby hurry along the var, intent upon their business of the hour.

The windowless facade of an alabaster villa is lit by the glow of several lanterns, which swing from lamppost set along the var.  A path of flat, pewter-colored stone slabs leads between the street and the white building.
The windowless facade of an alabaster villa sits back behind a row of lamppost set along the var.  A path of flat, pewter-colored stone slabs leads between the street and the white building.
title: [Ta'Vaalor, Emaereld Var]
